        <h3 class="pcr-ws-card__title">Cafes &amp; Bakeries</h3>
        <ul class="pcr-ws-card__list">
          <li>Custom menu development and dial-in support</li>
          <li>On-site barista training and workflow optimization</li>
          <li>Whole bean and ground options in every roast level</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="pcr-ws-card">
        <div class="pcr-ws-card__icon" aria-hidden="true">🏢</div>
        <h3 class="pcr-ws-card__title">Offices &amp; Workplaces</h3>
        <ul class="pcr-ws-card__list">
          <li>Premium perks to attract and retain top talent</li>
          <li>Automated standing orders and low-maintenance setups</li>
          <li>Flexible formats — whole bean, ground, or portion packs</li>
        </ul>
