  </div>
</section>

{%- comment -%} ══════════════════════════════════════════
  3. VALUE PROPS
══════════════════════════════════════════ {%- endcomment -%}
<section class="pcr-ws-section pcr-ws-value bg-stone">
  <div class="page-width">
    <div class="pcr-ws-value__layout">
      <div class="pcr-ws-value__copy">
        <h2 class="pcr-ws-section__title pcr-ws-section__title--left">More Than Just Coffee Beans</h2>
        <p class="pcr-ws-value__lead">We know a successful coffee program requires reliability. That's why we focus on quality control, training, and making the ordering process completely stress-free for your team.</p>
        <div class="pcr-ws-value__benefits">
          <div class="pcr-ws-benefit">
            <div class="pcr-ws-benefit__icon" aria-hidden="true">🚚</div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="pcr-ws-benefit__title">Freshness Guaranteed</h4>
              <p class="pcr-ws-benefit__desc">Strict roast-to-order schedules. We roast weekly and ship within 48 hours to ensure every bag arrives at peak flavor.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="pcr-ws-benefit">
            <div class="pcr-ws-benefit__icon" aria-hidden="true">🔧</div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="pcr-ws-benefit__title">Comprehensive Support</h4>
              <p class="pcr-ws-benefit__desc">From equipment consulting to emergency dial-in help, our team acts as an extension of your staff — not just a supplier.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="pcr-ws-benefit">
            <div class="pcr-ws-benefit__icon" aria-hidden="true">⚙️</div>
            <div>
              <h4 class="pcr-ws-benefit__title">Operational Ease</h4>
              <p class="pcr-ws-benefit__desc">Flexible ordering, predictable delivery windows, and standing order options. Less time managing coffee, more time on your business.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="pcr-ws-value__image">
        {%- if section.settings.value_image != blank -%}
          <img
            src="{{ section.settings.value_image | image_url: width: 900 }}"
            srcset="{{ section.settings.value_image | image_url: width: 600 }} 600w, {{ section.settings.value_image | image_url: width: 900 }} 900w"
            sizes="(min-width: 1024px) 45vw, 100vw"
            alt="{{ section.settings.value_image.alt | default: 'Barista pouring coffee' | escape }}"
            loading="lazy"
            class="pcr-ws-value__img"
          >
        {%- else -%}
          <div class="pcr-ws-value__img-placeholder">{{ 'image' | placeholder_svg_tag: 'placeholder-svg' }}</div>
        {%- endif -%}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{%- comment -%} ══════════════════════════════════════════
  4. PROGRAM STEPS
══════════════════════════════════════════ {%- endcomment -%}
<section class="pcr-ws-section pcr-ws-steps bg-white">
  <div class="page-width">
    <div class="pcr-ws-section__header">
      <h2 class="pcr-ws-section__title">How the Program Works</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="pcr-ws-grid pcr-ws-grid--4">
      <div class="pcr-ws-step">
        <div class="pcr-ws-step__number" aria-hidden="true">01</div>
        <h3 class="pcr-ws-step__title">Inquire &amp; Taste</h3>
        <p class="pcr-ws-step__desc">Fill out the form below. We'll send you a curated sample kit tailored to your equipment and volume needs.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pcr-ws-step">
        <div class="pcr-ws-step__number" aria-hidden="true">02</div>
        <h3 class="pcr-ws-step__title">Program Design</h3>
        <p class="pcr-ws-step__desc">We help you select the right blends, determine volume needs, and source equipment if necessary.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pcr-ws-step">
        <div class="pcr-ws-step__number" aria-hidden="true">03</div>
        <h3 class="pcr-ws-step__title">Staff Training</h3>
        <p class="pcr-ws-step__desc">Before your first order ships, we train your team on dialing in espresso and maintaining quality day-to-day.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pcr-ws-step">
        <div class="pcr-ws-step__number" aria-hidden="true">04</div>
        <h3 class="pcr-ws-step__title">Weekly Routine</h3>
        <p class="pcr-ws-step__desc">Order by Sunday night. We roast Monday and ship by Wednesday — fresh coffee, every week, on schedule.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{%- comment -%} ══════════════════════════════════════════
